---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, COMPANY_NAME } from '../consts';
---

<BaseHead title={`About Us - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Hermetrix Technologies is a New Zealand-based cybersecurity company specializing in secure communications and compliance guidance for the Asia-Pacific region." />

<Header />
<main>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About Hermetrix Technologies</h1>
			<p class="tagline">Building Trust Through Security Expertise</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="mission">
				<h2>Our Mission</h2>
				<p>Hermetrix Technologies exists to provide strategic operational security consulting for businesses that understand protection goes beyond IT. We help security-conscious leaders identify and address the human, process, and strategic vulnerabilities that traditional cybersecurity misses.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="story">
				<h2>Our Focus</h2>
				<p>Founded in New Zealand, Hermetrix Technologies recognizes the unique security challenges faced by organizations in the APAC region. We specialize in understanding both international security standards and local compliance frameworks to provide relevant, effective security guidance.</p>
				
				<p>Our approach is built on three core principles:</p>
				
				<div class="principles">
					<div class="principle">
						<h3>Security-First Mindset</h3>
						<p>Every solution we recommend or implement is evaluated against its security merits and certification status first.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="principle">
						<h3>Practical Guidance</h3>
						<p>We focus on helping organizations understand and work toward security goals through achievable steps and appropriate solutions.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="principle">
						<h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
						<p>The security landscape evolves constantly. We maintain our expertise to provide current, relevant advice.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>



			<div class="approach">
				<h2>Our Approach to Security</h2>
				<p>At Hermetrix Technologies, we believe effective security requires understanding both the technical requirements and the operational context. We help organizations:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Understand complex security frameworks like NZISM and PSR</li>
					<li>Identify appropriate certified security products</li>
					<li>Implement solutions that balance security and usability</li>
					<li>Develop sustainable security practices</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="disclaimer">
				<h3>Our Commitment to Transparency</h3>
				<p><strong>Hermetrix Technologies is a registered New Zealand company providing security consulting and implementation services.</strong> We are not a government agency and cannot provide official security clearances or compliance certifications.</p>
				<p>We work with commercially available, certified security products and provide guidance to help organizations navigate security requirements. Official certifications and formal compliance status must be obtained through appropriate government channels.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Ready to Enhance Your Security?</h2>
				<p>Contact us to discuss how we can help your organization achieve its security objectives.</p>
				<div class="contact-methods">
					<a href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz" class="btn primary">Get in Touch</a>
					<a href="/services" class="btn secondary">Our Services</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>
<Footer />

<style>
	/* Full-screen layout */
	body {
		margin: 0;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	main {
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	/* Hero Section - Full viewport */
	.hero {
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1419 0%, #1a365d 50%, #2d3748 100%);
		color: white;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		width: 100vw;
		margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
	}

	.hero::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
					radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.hero > .container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		padding: 0 2rem;
		max-width: 1200px;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
		text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #90cdf4;
	}

	/* About Content - Full screen sections */
	.about-content {
		flex: 1;
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		background: var(--bg-secondary);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.mission {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto 5rem;
	}

	.mission h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 2.8rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.mission p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #4a5568;
	}

	.story {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto 5rem;
	}

	.story h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.story p {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.principles {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}

	.principle {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.principle::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-dark));
	}

	.principle:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 45px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
		border-color: var(--accent);
	}

	.principle h3 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.principle p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.values {
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto 5rem;
	}

	.values h2 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.value {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border-radius: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.value:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
		border-color: var(--accent);
	}

	.value h3 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.value p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.approach {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto 5rem;
	}

	.approach h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.approach p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.approach ul {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}

	.approach li {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.approach li::before {
		content: 'â†’';
		position: absolute;
		left: -1.5rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.disclaimer {
		background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
		border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		margin: 4rem auto;
		max-width: 1200px;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
	}

	.disclaimer h3 {
		color: #ffc107;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.5);
	}

	.disclaimer p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		background: var(--bg-primary);
		color: white;
		min-height: 60vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.cta-section h2 {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: #90cdf4;
		font-size: 2.8rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.cta-section p {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.contact-methods {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #0a0a0a;
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.btn.primary:hover {
		background: var(--accent-dark);
		box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.6);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.btn.secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--accent);
		border-color: var(--accent);
		box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.btn.secondary:hover {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #0a0a0a;
		box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.container {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: none;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 4rem;
		}
		.tagline {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.mission h2,
		.story h2,
		.approach h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		.cta-section h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
			min-height: 90vh;
		}
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.about-content {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
			min-height: auto;
		}
		.mission {
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}
		.mission h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.story h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.approach h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.contact-methods {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
		.btn {
			width: 250px;
		}
		.principles,
		.values-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
		.cta-section {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
			min-height: auto;
		}
		.cta-section h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
		.mission h2,
		.values h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.cta-section h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.btn {
			padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
